(OOC: Sorry haven't posted, I got grounded from the net for two days, aaahhh!!)

*Teltoli looked down from her vantage point in the air down onto the beach. She sighed and tipped her wings downwards, diving to the ground until she landed beside Carnage with a soft thud on the sand. Using her scanners, she too could sense the Maximal Energy Signatures, but not the Base. She looked over the vast blue waters*

"Oh great. Dead end! But.. the Signatures are real close.. and where did the clone go to?"

*She rolls her eyes, and laughs. Teltoli wondered what the clones real name was, it would be a whole lot easier. She looks back up at Carnage for a second, with a slightly puzzled expression on her face*

"Carnage, when we DO find the Maximals, have you ever considered what your going to do after that? I mean, apart from killing Megatron?"
